2.Conny Freyer, Digital by Design, Thames & Hudson, 2008.
3.Steve Dixon, Digital Performance, MIT,London, 2007.
4.Susan Kozel, Closer-Performance, Technologies, Phenomenology, MIT,London, 2007.



參考教材
1.Frank Popper, From Technological to Virtual Art, MIT, London, 2007.
2.Lev Manovich, The Language of New Media, MIT Press,2002.





